pageProduct.name: Aussie Bodies Lo Carb Whipped Peanut Butter 50g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

15g PROTEIN
1.9g SUGARS
HIGH FIBRE
No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

Our Pro-active Nutrition products help your shape body from the inside out. Since 1991

Product Claims: 15g PROTEIN, 1.9g SUGARS, HIGH FIBRE, No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

Size: 50g

Flavour: Whipped Peanut Butter

Serving Size: 50g

Servings Per Pack: 1

KEY FEATURES

• Proactive Nutrition
• Great Tasting
• Guilt-Free Indulgence
• Source of Fibre
• Source of Protein

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Aussie Bodies® Protein Blend (26%) [Calcium Caseinate (Milk), Whey Protein Isolate (Milk), Soy Protein Isolate, Emulsifiers (Soy Lecithin, Mono- and Di-glycerides of Fatty Acids)], Protein Milk Chocolate (22%) (Cocoa Butter, Milk Solids, Sweeteners (Erythritol, Monk Fruit Extract, Steviol Glycosides), Soy Protein Isolate, Cocoa Mass, Inulin, Emulsifiers (Soy Lecithin), Natural Flavour), Sweetener (Polydextrose), Sweetener (Sorbitol), Humectant (Glycerol), Peanut Butter Layer (7%) (Peanut Butter (14%), Inulin, Vegetable Fat, Peanut Flour, Pea Protein Isolate, Stabilisers (Cellulose Microcrystalline, Locust Bean Gum, Xanthan Gum), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Salt, Natural Flavour), Roasted Peanuts (4%), Peanut Butter (1.5%), Vegetable Oil, Peanut Flour, Salt, Burnt Sugar Syrup, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin).

Contains: Contains: Milk, Soy and Peanuts.
May Contain: Cereals Containing Gluten (Wheat, Oats), Tree Nuts (Almonds, Hazelnuts) and Sesame Seeds.

Allergen Contains: Milk| Peanuts| Soy

Allergen May Be Present: Almonds| Hazelnuts| Oats| Sesame Seeds| Tree Nuts| Wheat| Cereals Containing Gluten

Directions

Store in a cool, dry place, below 30°C. Keep out of direct sunlight.
